Package: bwe
Type: Package
Title: Estimates Bayesian Word Embeddings
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-11-12
Author: Adam Lauretig
Maintainer: Adam Lauretig <adlauretig@gmail.com>
Description: This package implements a Bayesian word embedding model, estimated with variational inference. It also allows the user to rotate embeddings, identifying them in the manner suggested by Rivers (2003).
